---
title: "Formation of Trapped Surfaces for the Einstein–Maxwell–Charged Scalar Field System (joint with Dawei Shen)"
collection: publications
date: 2025-04-28
venue: ""
excerpt: "We prove scale-critical trapped surface formation for the Einstein–Maxwell–charged scalar field system."
paperurl: "https://arxiv.org/abs/2504.19976"
area: gr
status: preprint
---

In this paper, we prove a scale-critical trapped surface formation result for the Einstein–Maxwell–charged scalar field system without symmetry assumptions, together with a nontrivial charging process along past null infinity.
